  "title": "EVENTS EXECUTIVE (ROADSHOW)",
  "description": "<h2>🎯 Events Executive (Full-Time)</h2><p><em>Entry Level Welcome | Hands-On | Growth Opportunities</em></p><p>Want a role that’s fast-paced, people-focused, and never boring?</p><p>Join us as an <strong>Events Executive</strong> and gain real experience running events and roadshows from start to finish.<br /></p><h3>🚀 What You Can Expect</h3><p>• Plan and execute events & roadshows<br />• Be on-site to manage setup, operations, and wrap-up<br />• Work with teams and clients to deliver smooth, successful events<br />• Learn leadership, communication, and problem-solving skills<br /></p><h3>🌟 We’re Looking For</h3><p>• Driven, hardworking individuals with a positive attitude<br />• Strong communication skills and willingness to learn<br />• Able to thrive in a dynamic, high-energy environment</p><p><strong>✨ No experience required — training provided.</strong></p><p><em>Build confidence, skills, and a career with us!!</em></p>",
